snippet.title: Confrontation, Emotions & The End of The Last of Us: Part II | Hard | PS5
snippet.description:
We return to the Confrontation and experience a whole lot of emotions as we reach the End of The Last of Us Part II. 

I am playing Hard Mode on the PS5.

To everyone who watched this series, who has joined in on the discussions in the comments and who has become a part of this community through the journey of The Last of Us: Thank you.

https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLxHhV3NungnDHlvy_vOwspR9xChO6JKu1
